title: No FEE Watertown,$2100,4 rooms, free pkg.for 2 small cars
posting_body: ['Watertown, 4 rooms, NO FEE.', 'Free parking for 2 small cars at your back door.', '$2100 plus utilities.', 'Available now.', 'First floor of a 2 family house, owner occupied.', 'Sunny rooms with high ceilings and oak floors original to the 1895 house; living room, eat in kitchen, bedroom with walk in closet, bathroom shower only, and another room could be a dining room or office or another bedroom and a good size entrance hall; 2 porches; gas heat and stove, seconds to bus to Harvard or Watertown Squares; walk to stores, restaurants, Arsenal Yards, or to the Charles River; yard for a small garden or a grille; and small area for storage in the cellar.', 'No dogs, No Cats; No smoking, No hook ups for washer/drier; Several laundromats walking distance; no dishwasher.', 'Quiet and safe neighborhood.', 'Application, credit check and reference check needed.', 'First month’s rent and security deposit of 1 month at time of  Tenant at will Agreement signed, Please call 617-924-2978 with questions or to arrange a viewing and if voice mail picks up, leave your name and number and I will return your call.', 'Or use your PERSONAL OR BUSINESS EMAIL ADDRESS.', 'I do not respond to blind emails because of spam.']
